>theta = s/r
>theta= 50/10 = 5 radians

Thanks for writing to Ask Dr. Math, Diana!

Your Thoughts above are right on target!  The answer is, indeed, 5
radians, or 900/Pi degrees.

Feel free to reply if I can help further with this question.


